params.name: input_audio
params.description: Raw audio which will be encoded to its discrete representation using the codebook. The closest codeform the codebook will be computed for each sequence of samples.

params.name: start_level
params.description: Level at which the encoding process will start. Default to 0.

params.name: end_level
params.description: Level at which the encoding process will start. Default to None.

params.name: bs_chunks
params.description: Number of chunks of raw audio to process at the same time.
